<td align="center"><b>
<i>Perdita halictoides</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">Smith, 1853</font></b><br>
<small><i>Perdita sexmaculata var punctata </i>Cockerell, 1896; <i>Perdita maura </i>Cockerell, 1901; <i>Perdita bisignata </i>Cockerell, 1922</small><p>
